  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-EP-02 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification is performed. This synthetic adversarial package introduces W-EP-02: the primary hemolysis validation result carries a detailed prose narrative describing the experimental campaign and CFD comparison but omits the structured prov:wasGeneratedBy link to its generation Activity. A reviewer may assume the narrative substitutes for the structured provenance reference.",
