      "prov:wasGeneratedBy": "https://uofa.net/synth/activity/mesh-gci-study-run-2025q3",
      "description": "Grid convergence index study over three systematically refined meshes (3.1M, 8.7M, 14.2M cells) for the VAD impeller passage. GCI on NIH quantity of interest is 1.78%, satisfying the required threshold of less than 3% for credibility level 3 discretization error factor."
    },
    {
